        <tr><td>
<a class="key" href="../index.htm"><div  data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Shortcut to Tutus Data AB (Sweden)" class="key">Tutus</div></a><a class="key" href="../../ip.htm#ip"><div  data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Shortcut to Internet Protocol VPN encryptors" class="key">IP</div></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;        <div style="height: 20px;"></div>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          <b>F&#228;rist A100</b>
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
<b>Portable VPN encryptor</b>
<br />
<br />
<b>Micro F&#228;rist A100M2</b>, also known as <b>F&#228;rist A100</b> or <b>F&#228;rist Micro</b>, <sup><font color="#FF8800">1</font></sup>
is a pocket <span class="short" aria-label="Virtual Private Network" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../ip.htm" class="short" >VPN</a></span> <a href="../../ip.htm"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: encryptor">encryptor</span></a>, developed in 2007 by <a href="../index.htm"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: Tutus Data AB">Tutus Data AB</span></a>
in Danderyd (Sweden). It allows a <a href="../../../pc"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: Personal Computer">Personal Computer</span></a> (<span class="short" aria-label="Personal Computer" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../../pc" class="short" >PC</a></span>) with an
Ethernet interface &mdash; typically a laptop &mdash;
to be connected to a trusted remote network,
using insecure public infrastructure &ndash; such as the internet &ndash;
as the transport medium, at 1 Mb/s.
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
The device, shown in the image on the right,
is ideally suited for travelling business people.
It is housed in an aluminium and carbon fibre enclo&shy;sure that
measures just 135 &#215; 35 &#215; 24 mm and weighs no more than 92 grams.
At the time of its conception, it was arguably the smallest pro&shy;fessional
<span class="short" aria-label="Virtual Private Network" data-balloon-pos="up"><a href="../../ip.htm" class="short" >VPN</a></span> encryption device in the world.
<br />
<br />
There are no controls or indicators, just three connectors:
(1) an RJ45 socket for connection of the local device, or host,
(2) an RJ45 socket for connection of the (insecure) network, and (3)
a circular socket for connecting a power adapter.
          </font></td>
          <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
          <td align=center valign=top width=100>
          <table 
           border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tr><td align="center" valign=top>
<a href="img/304235/000/full.jpg">            <div style="position: relative;" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Micro Färist A1000 - top view">
<a href="img/304235/000/full.jpg">            <div style="position: relative;" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Micro Färist A1000 - top view">
            <img src="img/304235/000/small.jpg"
             style="
             max-width: 618px;
            "
             align="left"
             vspace="4"
             alt="Micro Färist A1000 - top view"
             border=0
             width=298 height=200
             />
            </div>
            </a>
            </td></tr><tr><td align=center>
          </td></tr></table>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
The device can be configured via a web interface through the Host ethernet
port, using nothing more than a standard browser and HTTPS.
The device is part of the F&#228;rist VPN family of secure <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Internet Protocol">IP</span> products,
and has meanwhile been suc&shy;ceeded by newer generations, such as the
F&#228;rist Micro A410 and the M300 military variant, both of which have a maximum
throughput of 15 Mb/s.
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width="50" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr>
        <td style="border-top: 1px solid #aaa;"><img src="../img/blank.gif" width="1" height="5"/></td>
        </tr></table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr><td>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#888888><small>
          <ol>
          <li>
<b>F&#228;rist</b> is the Swedish word for 'cattle-guard'.
          </ol>
          </small></font></td></tr>
