hange</div><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Rivest-Shamir-Adleman (encryption algorithm)">RSA</span>            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Standards</div>IPv4, IPSEC ESP (RFC 2406) in tunnel mode            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Processor</div>Intel X-scale <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Advanced RISC Machines">ARM</span>, 200 MHz            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Random Access Memory">RAM</span></div>64MB            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;"><span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Read-Only Memory">ROM</span></div>16MB (Flash)            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Storage</div>MicroSC card reader            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Dimensions</div>135 &#215; 35 &#215; 24 mm            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:100px;">Weight</div>92 g          </ul>
